00:23:38,000 --> 00:23:42,000
otherwise would have been allowed to do.

251
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:46,000
The men had no restrictions on at all.

252
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:50,000
And in my house there was a real

253
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:54,000
strongly enforced study hours from 7 to 9.

254
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:58,000
The house was supposed to be very quiet and it was.

255
00:23:58,000 --> 00:24:04,000
So I could name you

256
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:10,000
a flourish to those times.

257
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:12,000
That is studied.

258
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:14,000
The other thing I can come in on,

259
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:18,000
there was no alcohol available anywhere.

260
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:20,000
Not in town.

261
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:23,000
I think there was something like a two-mile rule.

262
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:28,000
There would be no retail outlet for alcohol

263
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:33,000
within two miles of the campus.

